 Contact Bright  Horizons 
 



Find a Bright Horizons Center or School


Use the Bright Horizons locator to find a child care center or school near you.



Parent Customer Service


For general information and comments, please contact parents@brighthorizons.com or call 866-854-1958.


Full- or Part-Time Care


For information on center locations or enrollment information, please contact familysolutions@brighthorizons.com or call 877-624-4532.


Back-Up Care


If you are a parent from a client company that participates in a Bright Horizons back-up care program and you are looking for back-up care, please contact us at 877-BH-CARES or visit us here.


New Center Information


For questions or information on new center openings please contact Welcome@brighthorizons.com.


Human Resources


For Career Opportunities in the United States and Canada, please see the careers section of our site.
If you are an employee and have concerns regarding your employment or practices at your location, please e-mail hrconcerns@brighthorizons.com.

For career opportunities or HR questions in Europe, please contact europe.recruitment@brighthorizons.com.


For Benefit and Payroll Information, please visit the Benefits and Payroll Contacts page.


Client Services


For information on developing dependent care programs for your organization or to inquire about our work/life consulting services, contact Bright Horizons Client Services or call 800-453-9383.


Acquisitions


For information about the potential for your child care or early education program to become a part of our organization, please visit www.brighthorizons.com/acquisitions.


World Headquarters


Bright Horizons Family Solutions
200 Talcott Avenue South
Watertown, MA 02472
617-673-8000
Directions to Our World Headquarters Office



